00:06:12.414 --> 00:06:14.231
It's about 80 minutes long.

00:06:14.255 --> 00:06:15.660
(Laughter)

00:06:15.684 --> 00:06:18.236
No, no, no. It's four minutes long.

00:06:18.260 --> 00:06:21.568
And I want to first rehearse
with you your whistling.

00:06:22.427 --> 00:06:24.179
Yes, so I whistle the tone.

00:06:24.203 --> 00:06:26.236
(Whistling)

00:06:26.260 --> 00:06:28.476
(Laughter)

00:06:28.608 --> 00:06:30.622
Sorry, I forgot one thing --

00:06:31.423 --> 00:06:33.992
