00:06:56.589 --> 00:06:57.948
This is very promising.

00:06:57.972 --> 00:06:59.159
(Laughter)

00:06:59.183 --> 00:07:00.524
This is very promising.

00:07:00.548 --> 00:07:03.236
I'll ask the technicians
to start the music.

00:07:03.260 --> 00:07:06.498
And if it's started,
I just point where you whistle along,

00:07:06.522 --> 00:07:08.095
and we will see what happens.

00:07:08.119 --> 00:07:10.254
(Laughter)

00:07:13.883 --> 00:07:17.906
Oh, I'm so sorry, technicians.

00:07:17.930 --> 00:07:22.159
(Laughter)

00:07:22.183 --> 00:07:23.381
I'm so used to that.

00:07:23.405 --> 00:07:24.429
(Laughter)

00:07:24.453 --> 00:07:25.778
I start it myself.

00:07:25.802 --> 00:07:26.963
(Laughter)

00:07:26.987 --> 00:07:28.236
OK, here it is.

00:07:28.260 --> 00:07:31.609
(Laughter)

00:07:31.633 --> 00:07:33.579
